club.seedymusic.jpa.bean

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • club.seedymusic.jpa.bean.Order

  • @Entity
public class Order
extends java.lang.Object

    Order Class

    This class is the entity bean used by the Java Persistence API. It represents an Order entry in the database.

    Version:
    Oct 9, 2017 Created this class.
    Author:
    Karim Sultan
